metadata.name: Pepe Say Anything
metadata.description:
A 4k meme video in a perfect loop — depicting a contemporary cliché Pepe The Frog sporting a nostalgic moment from the 1989 movie Say Anything.

Nostalgia & Cliché (Noché) ———  
Nostalgia & Cliché is a series of 4k videos sporting nostalgic moments from the 80s & 90s, a bit of a pop culture cliché, and some psychedelic animations.  
Though had to kick off the series with Pepe Meme. But of course, it's not gonna be about just Pepe. 

GIVEAWAY ———  
Gonna airdrop the next edition in this series to all folks who mint multiples of this edition.

Please support me by following me on Twitter @_fets_luck_
